Articles.Content:
1 hour ago, Dr. Kerbal said:

Hello. Im just wondering. If you think about it, a mission to Eeloo isn't that hard with SRBs as it may seem. I mean expect for these:

  • Getting to LKO
  • Eeloo Transfer
  • COrrection Burns to Eeloo
  • Eeloo orbit
  • Eeloo Landing
  • Eeloo takeoff
  • Eeloo to Kerbin Trasnfer
  • KErbin reentry (woo!)

The parachuting down is easy. 

So it’s hard instead of insanely hard?
